WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:02.091
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:02.091 --> 00:00:04.286
Thank you for joining me today.

00:00:04.286 --> 00:00:06.297
Truly, I'm so glad you're here.

00:00:06.297 --> 00:00:09.420
You know, yesterday was a wow.

00:00:09.420 --> 00:00:15.440
I will forever be changed by what happened yesterday.

00:00:15.440 --> 00:00:22.960
And I know a lot of people, because they weren't seeing it and I was trying to describe what I was seeing, don't get it a lot.

00:00:22.960 --> 00:00:26.799
And the comment section kind of goes along with that.

00:00:26.799 --> 00:00:32.880
But today, I'm going to make it clear for you to let you understand what the Lord was showing me.

00:00:33.920 --> 00:00:42.000
We were just singing 'The Lord is here' like you saw, and all of a sudden I saw the Lord said, 'I'm here, Brandon.

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:46.267
' And I heard Him so clear and I said, 'Oh, the Lord is here.

00:00:46.267 --> 00:00:47.554
The Lord is here.

00:00:49.040 --> 00:00:49.640
The presence of the Lord is filling my house.

00:00:49.640 --> 00:00:51.760
' And it was the glory.

00:01:04.790 --> 00:01:05.060
I could feel the glory.

00:01:08.319 --> 00:01:08.559
Diana was sitting on the other side of the camera yesterday.

00:01:08.559 --> 00:01:10.660
Braden was doing the editing, remember?

00:01:14.826 --> 00:01:22.136
She fell out and she was laying right here in the middle of the floor, and she was weeping before the Lord, but she started smelling the fragrance of the Father like she always does.

00:01:28.729 --> 00:01:35.177
When the presence of the Lord fills the room, Diana will smell this fragrance of the Lord and it smells like sweet honeysuckle and all these other things that she describes, and it's absolutely glorious.

00:01:52.159 --> 00:01:52.679
But I've never really smelled it, only glimpses.

00:01:52.679 --> 00:01:58.719
It will come and it fades away, and I can smell it, but it's never like it is for her.

00:02:01.751 --> 00:02:04.500
But all of a sudden, when I was telling you I was hearing somebody singing, people said, 'Oh, Brandon, you heard me singing.

00:02:04.500 --> 00:02:11.348
' No, I wasn't hearing something in the natural; I was hearing in the spirit.

00:02:15.790 --> 00:02:21.680
And all of a sudden, I heard them singing the song that I was singing: 'From glory to glory, He's changing us, changing us.

00:02:21.680 --> 00:02:24.371
' But it was multiple voices, and I froze.

00:02:24.371 --> 00:02:31.640
That's why I was—it freaked me out a little bit because I thought, 'Well, my goodness, Diana, you're singing, too.

00:02:31.640 --> 00:02:39.200
' But you know, she was laying down there, but it sounded like it was right here, right here, everywhere.

00:02:43.900 --> 00:02:44.200
And all of us: 'From glory to glory, He's changing us.

00:02:44.200 --> 00:02:50.750
' But I noticed one of the voices, and everybody goes, 'Who is Sister Lucy?

00:02:50.750 --> 00:02:53.828
' Her name is Lucy Harriott, I believe, is her name.

00:02:59.671 --> 00:03:00.222
She is a lady that used to pray as a prayer warrior.

00:03:02.139 --> 00:03:05.307
And she is the twin sister of Lynn Hammond, who has a church up in Minneapolis, Minnesota.

00:03:06.550 --> 00:03:07.960
And it's called Living Word Church.

00:03:07.960 --> 00:03:10.939
Living Word, I believe, is the church's name.

00:03:22.000 --> 00:03:22.213
And they have a great congregation.

00:03:22.213 --> 00:03:23.280
They're a spirit-filled church.

00:03:23.280 --> 00:03:25.389
They love the Lord and are really on fire.

00:03:25.389 --> 00:03:26.823
They're prayer warriors.

00:03:26.823 --> 00:03:29.272
They're a great prayer church.

00:03:29.272 --> 00:03:31.280
Her husband is Mimmon.

00:03:34.580 --> 00:03:36.391
And if you're not familiar with it, I'd encourage you to look them up.

00:03:36.391 --> 00:03:37.280
They're great people.

00:03:37.280 --> 00:03:41.120
So, I was hearing her when she used to be alive.

00:03:41.440 --> 00:03:46.777
I heard old tapes and old CDs and things from back in the day.

00:03:57.240 --> 00:03:57.680
And I remember her voice, and I went, 'Diana, that's Lucy.

00:04:04.587 --> 00:04:04.960
I hear Lucy.

00:04:04.960 --> 00:04:12.675
' And Diana knew who it was because we love to listen to her old stuff from when she was alive.

00:04:12.675 --> 00:04:14.710
She passed away, I believe it was 2010.

00:04:14.710 --> 00:04:20.809
Well, I could hear the voice of Lucy and I was like, 'What in the world is that?

00:04:20.809 --> 00:04:23.463
' because I knew it was her voice.

00:04:24.171 --> 00:04:30.1000
And all of a sudden, I saw like this circle before my eye right here, right here.

00:04:30.1000 --> 00:04:34.091
It went poof and it popped out.

00:04:53.750 --> 00:04:54.140
It looked like a tunnel that was in the spirit realm right before my face.

00:04:54.140 --> 00:05:02.023
And I could see the edges of this tunnel that looked like clouds, almost like you would see cotton candy.

00:05:02.023 --> 00:05:04.540
That's a good way to describe it.

00:05:04.770 --> 00:05:07.570
Like cotton candy—pink, purple cotton candy, fluffy, cloud-looking cotton candy.

00:05:11.387 --> 00:05:11.813
And it was on the walls of this tunnel.

00:05:27.760 --> 00:05:27.1000
And as it went up, it had ridges.

00:05:27.1000 --> 00:05:38.610
But as I kept looking through it, the tunnel started moving and my spiritual eyes were moving with it, and I could see.

00:05:38.610 --> 00:05:46.210
And all of a sudden, I went through the tunnel up to where it ended, and there was a light there.

00:05:46.210 --> 00:05:47.759
Everything was lit up.

00:05:47.759 --> 00:05:54.640
I'm going to tell you that there was no darkness at all.

00:05:54.640 --> 00:06:04.000
But the light became brighter, and I looked through the tunnel, and then I could hear them singing even louder: 'From glory to glory.

00:06:04.000 --> 00:06:08.533
' And I asked the Father, 'What is this?

00:06:08.533 --> 00:06:12.303
' He said, 'This is the great cloud of witnesses.

00:06:12.303 --> 00:06:18.240
' All of a sudden, I could see everything within probably a 20-foot radius.

00:06:42.150 --> 00:06:42.381
I could see this massive tree, a beautiful oak tree with beautiful leaves on it that had no darkness on them or shadows at all.

00:06:50.960 --> 00:06:51.316
The leaves were all different kinds of shades of green, but there was no darkness.

00:06:51.316 --> 00:06:59.306
Like, you know, when you see leaves on top of each other, there are shadows on there, but there were no shadows on this tree.

00:07:03.240 --> 00:07:06.840
And the wood was beautiful, vibrant wood on this tree trunk, okay?

00:07:06.840 --> 00:07:10.320
I saw green grass all around.

00:07:10.320 --> 00:07:18.960
That was the first thing I saw because the tree was the tallest.

00:07:34.975 --> 00:07:35.280
As I'm coming up through this, I could see the tree.

00:07:35.280 --> 00:07:45.840
But then I looked down, and as I'm coming up through this hole, this thing, whatever this was, this portal, I could see Lucy sitting in a rocking chair.

00:07:58.287 --> 00:07:58.559
And she had her head down like this, and she was rocking and she was praying.

00:08:06.365 --> 00:08:06.674
She was praying in this rocking chair.

00:08:11.280 --> 00:08:15.778
And then on the right side of her, right here, was Brother Halverson, who is another amazing prayer warrior in his time on the earth.

00:08:15.778 --> 00:08:18.284
He's no longer here either.

00:08:18.284 --> 00:08:22.079
And he was sitting next to her right here.

00:08:30.060 --> 00:08:30.400
And Brother Halverson was praying and he was saying, 'Minnesota, Minnesota.

00:08:30.400 --> 00:08:32.000
' And he was praying out Minnesota.

00:08:32.960 --> 00:08:34.560
And they were praying together about Minnesota.

00:08:34.560 --> 00:08:40.986
And I could hear them praying about Minnesota, and I'll get to that more in a minute.

00:08:40.986 --> 00:08:45.696
Jeanie Wilkerson, who is another major prayer warrior, was sitting next to Brother Halverson.

00:08:50.1000 --> 00:08:58.596
On this side was Rachel Teafatiller, who is another amazing prayer warrior in the time back in the 1950s, 1940s.

00:08:58.596 --> 00:09:06.229
She was a prayer warrior at Collinsville where I go to church, and she went home to be with the Lord.

00:09:06.229 --> 00:09:09.862
She's praying next to Jeanie Wilkerson, who was friends with Kenneth E.

00:09:09.862 --> 00:09:13.341
Hagin and she prayed in the camp meetings and all kinds of stuff.

00:09:13.341 --> 00:09:17.440
She was a great prayer warrior, but they were so young.

00:09:17.440 --> 00:09:20.360
This was Jeanie Wilkerson, Rachel Teafatiller, and then Sister Woodworth-Etter.

00:09:20.360 --> 00:09:25.429
Sister, I know I probably butchered the lady's name, but Sister Woodworth-Etter was sitting next to Rachel Teafatiller.

00:09:25.429 --> 00:09:30.460
How I knew because I said, 'Lord, who is this lady with the double bun?

00:09:30.460 --> 00:09:39.480
' She had her hair up, big poofy Pentecostal hair, and it was a bun on top of a bun.

00:09:39.480 --> 00:09:43.786
And I thought, 'You never see that.

00:09:43.786 --> 00:09:51.733
' But she was wearing her hair as a bun on top of a bun, and she was very old-school Pentecostal looking—old-school.

00:10:00.286 --> 00:10:00.743
And I asked the Lord after—this is how I know.

00:10:00.743 --> 00:10:11.120
I was praying after it was over, after our prayer session, I said, 'Lord, what did you just show me?

00:10:11.120 --> 00:10:12.880
What was that?

00:10:12.880 --> 00:10:17.900
' He said, 'That's Sister Woodworth-Etter, Brandon.

00:10:17.900 --> 00:10:19.100
She's an elder.

00:10:19.100 --> 00:10:20.845
Go look her up.

00:10:20.845 --> 00:10:28.533
' So, I went and I had Diana—I said, 'Diana, would you look this name up?

00:10:28.533 --> 00:10:35.049
This is who the Lord said that other woman was, sitting next to Rachel Teafatiller.

00:10:35.049 --> 00:10:37.580
' And she looked, she goes, 'Oh my gosh.

00:10:37.580 --> 00:10:43.714
' Then there was another lady there, and I don't know who that was.

00:10:43.714 --> 00:10:45.360
I still don't.

00:10:45.360 --> 00:10:52.856
She was sitting, looking at Lucy, and I said, 'Lord, what are they doing?

00:10:52.856 --> 00:10:55.249
What are they doing?

00:10:55.249 --> 00:10:58.239
' after I could see all this stuff.

00:10:58.239 --> 00:11:11.253
But I don't say a lot of things that I'm saying, but I'm saying it in my spirit toward the Father, and you don't know I'm saying it because I'm talking to Him.

00:11:12.688 --> 00:11:14.008
And I said to Him, 'What are they doing?

00:11:14.008 --> 00:11:18.594
' He said to me, 'Brandon, this is a prayer group.

00:11:18.594 --> 00:11:21.501
' I'm like, 'A prayer group in heaven?

00:11:21.501 --> 00:11:23.279
Why are they praying?

00:11:23.279 --> 00:11:30.057
' He said, 'Brandon, they're praying on an assignment for the revival that's about to take place on the earth.

00:11:30.057 --> 00:11:30.940
' He said, 'They're assisting you.

00:11:30.940 --> 00:11:31.250
They're helping you.

00:11:31.250 --> 00:11:42.869
' I know the Bible says that Jesus is at the right hand making intercession for all of us, but I was like taken back by it because I was thinking, 'Is this biblical?

00:11:42.869 --> 00:11:48.220
' you know, because I don't know this in the Word, because I'm always questioning everything.

00:11:54.980 --> 00:11:56.360
But I know that as on earth, as it is in heaven, and that's the scripture that I'm going to go by, that they were praying in heaven and they're praying on the earth.

00:12:01.280 --> 00:12:01.680
And these people were praying.

00:12:08.022 --> 00:12:08.228
Were they crying?

00:12:08.228 --> 00:12:08.639
No.

00:12:08.639 --> 00:12:14.384
So I said, "Lord, what are they praying about?

00:12:24.046 --> 00:12:24.297
" And they were interceding for revival in Minnesota.

00:12:28.871 --> 00:12:29.147
I heard Brother Halverson kept praying for revival.

00:12:38.144 --> 00:12:38.912
And all of a sudden, Living Word Lynne Hammond's church—with Lucy as the head of the prayer group—she was sitting in a rocking chair.

00:12:38.912 --> 00:12:42.380
Now, I got to go back to this.

00:12:42.380 --> 00:12:45.010
What were the others sitting on?

00:12:45.010 --> 00:12:50.139
They were sitting on a patchwork quilt on top of the beautiful green grass.

00:12:52.240 --> 00:12:53.097
And each little square was purple and pastel colors.

00:12:53.097 --> 00:12:57.009
Beautiful pastel colors like Easter colors, beautiful Easter-like pastel spring colors.

00:12:58.120 --> 00:13:03.698
There was purple, blue, pink, and white, but it was all like these little squares.

00:13:04.027 --> 00:13:06.000
And there was a patchwork quilt.

00:13:06.309 --> 00:13:18.800
And on top of the purple squares, I could see beautiful little daisies with little white flowers with a yellow ring, a yellow little print on the inside of it.

00:13:27.973 --> 00:13:28.347
And they were all little bitty flowers on top of the beautiful purple squares.

00:13:41.965 --> 00:13:42.228
And on the blue squares were different things, but all the different flowers created a beautiful quilt that they were sitting on, praying.

00:13:57.600 --> 00:13:58.160
But at the corners of each of the squares where they joined together was a beautiful ribbon of yellow.

00:13:58.160 --> 00:14:07.013
A beautiful ribbon of yellow was at the corner of each four corners of all of the quilt pattern.

00:14:07.013 --> 00:14:19.427
It was like it ran up through, and I could see it, and at the edges was a beautiful embroidery of some kind of beautiful print that was around it, and it was so beautiful.

00:14:19.427 --> 00:14:23.703
But Lucy was sitting in a wooden rocking chair.

00:14:26.360 --> 00:14:29.040
It looked oak, and it was like an old one you would get at Cracker Barrel.

00:14:47.467 --> 00:14:47.876
You know, like if you're in America, we have a restaurant called Cracker Barrel, and they sell a wooden rocking chair that you sit on your porch with.

00:14:49.920 --> 00:14:52.500
And that's the kind of Southern rocking chair that it was.

00:14:52.500 --> 00:14:54.540
It's a real Southern thing.

00:14:54.540 --> 00:15:01.462
Wooden rocking chairs like this are what we have down in the South, and they sell them at Cracker Barrel and you can get them.

00:15:01.462 --> 00:15:03.502
That's the kind of wooden rocking chair Lucy was in.

00:15:03.502 --> 00:15:05.040
But she was at the edge of it.

00:15:05.040 --> 00:15:12.140
She wasn't leaning back in her chair; she was at the edge leaning forward, and Brother Halverson was leaning forward.

00:15:13.866 --> 00:15:18.766
And I could see Jeanie Wilkerson was leaning back, and the others, and they were all just interceding and praying for a revival in Minnesota.

00:15:18.766 --> 00:15:26.750
As they were praying, I could hear them saying Minnesota, praying for Lynne Hammond's church, which is Living Word, which I told you.

00:15:35.680 --> 00:15:35.920
And that's Lucy, her sister.

00:15:35.920 --> 00:15:37.839
But they were praying for this, right?

00:15:45.450 --> 00:15:47.199
And all of a sudden—I'm trying not to skip around—all of a sudden, I saw a massive fire break out inside of a Holy Ghost and fire—a wave of His glory hit that church.

00:15:53.920 --> 00:15:54.300
And the Lord spoke to me, and He said, "I visited this church in the '90s, Brandon.

00:15:54.300 --> 00:15:58.514
" He said, "But this was with Lynne and her husband.

00:16:03.099 --> 00:16:24.399
" And He said, "Brandon, I'm going to visit it with this new generation, and there will be a great move of My presence one more time on this church, and I will pour out My spirit, and there will be a mighty revival in Living Word as they were interceding for it.

00:16:24.399 --> 00:16:28.151
" And I saw it like echo all throughout Minnesota, and people were getting born again by the tens of thousands.

00:16:37.965 --> 00:16:38.217
The glory is coming, folks.

00:16:38.217 --> 00:16:40.983
But He was showing me hot spots.

00:16:46.624 --> 00:16:51.360
And as it became on fire, it became like a brush fire; it started spreading out.

00:16:51.867 --> 00:16:53.720
It didn't stay there on that church; it started spreading out.

00:16:55.120 --> 00:16:59.920
And there was charred ground on the land like you see when the fires are moving.

00:17:10.319 --> 00:17:10.524
And every one of the—I call them hot spots.

00:17:10.524 --> 00:17:15.413
There was a hot spot when I was praying; I saw it in Branson and Tulsa and Fort Worth.

00:17:15.413 --> 00:17:27.920
But then I looked to the east, and I saw hot spots popping up all over the east, Kentucky, Tennessee, all over the place.

00:17:28.880 --> 00:17:31.143
And He said, "The bluer the state...

00:17:31.143 --> 00:17:36.208
" Many said, "What are you talking about, the bluer the state?

00:17:49.314 --> 00:17:49.611
" He said, "The bluer the state, Brandon, which is Democrat, it's liberals.

00:17:49.611 --> 00:17:53.813
" He said, "The bluer the state, the greater the harvest.

00:17:53.813 --> 00:17:56.160
" That's what He said.

00:18:01.279 --> 00:18:02.296
"The bluer the state, son, the more liberal it is, the greater the harvest.

00:18:02.296 --> 00:18:07.831
Don't look at it as this dark blue, because the darker blue it is, the greater the harvest.

00:18:07.831 --> 00:18:09.591
" That's what the Father said.

00:18:11.009 --> 00:18:15.387
Because Minnesota is very blue, very liberal, and the Lord said, "The greater the blue, the greater the harvest.

00:18:15.387 --> 00:18:16.293
" Hallelujah!

00:18:16.293 --> 00:18:19.333
I tell you, I saw it.

00:18:20.760 --> 00:18:27.013
And then I looked to the west, and there were those hot spots popping up all over the place.

00:18:27.013 --> 00:18:36.480
They were all in Oregon, they were all in Washington, they were all in California, they were in Nevada, and they were popping up.

00:18:59.200 --> 00:18:59.547
And this is what He told me.

00:19:03.792 --> 00:19:03.976
You remember when I told you about the popcorn?

00:19:11.634 --> 00:19:11.897
He said, "You don't know where the next revival is going to start.

00:19:11.897 --> 00:19:20.240
If you go heat up a pan, son, with some coconut oil in it, and you watch the pan, you don't know which one's going to pop next.

00:19:20.240 --> 00:19:25.588
" He said, "That's the way this next revival is going to be.

00:19:25.588 --> 00:19:27.648
They're going to be popping all over the place.

00:19:27.648 --> 00:19:30.903
" He goes, "Because you're not going to control it.

00:19:40.697 --> 00:19:43.244
" A lot of people, when you have an Asbury or whatever, or a Brownsville or whatever, people try to control it after a while.

00:19:43.244 --> 00:19:56.822
"Well, you know, this is the way we should do it," and they try to limit God in how He's doing things.

00:19:56.822 --> 00:20:01.097
"Well, you know, it's getting out of hand.

00:20:01.097 --> 00:20:03.940
People are getting too radical; they're getting too noisy.

00:20:03.940 --> 00:20:11.947
So, we've got to kind of corral this.

00:20:18.600 --> 00:20:22.133
" And the Lord said, "You're not going to corral what's about to happen with your Pharisee thinking.

00:20:22.133 --> 00:20:26.400
God is going to have His way.

00:20:44.053 --> 00:20:44.546
" And I saw, as they were praying, their prayers—when we were praying together as a family—their prayers were rolling out of heaven, and they were popping me in the stomach.

00:20:45.725 --> 00:20:53.570
And I was groaning the prayer, and we were assisting each other in prayer for the nations, for revival around the world.

00:21:00.766 --> 00:21:02.194
And He said, "Brandon, you'll notice they won't get tired because they're not in their earthly body anymore.

00:21:02.194 --> 00:21:06.160
They're in their glorified body, so they can pray all the time.

00:21:06.160 --> 00:21:09.609
They don't go, 'I've got to take a break.

00:21:09.609 --> 00:21:11.386
We've got to have nighttime.

00:21:11.386 --> 00:21:13.537
We've got to go eat.

00:21:13.537 --> 00:21:18.427
' They were praying like there's no time.

00:21:18.427 --> 00:21:24.359
There's no time in heaven, do you understand?

00:21:24.359 --> 00:21:26.533
So, they're continually praying.

00:21:45.497 --> 00:21:45.749
They lose track of time because they're in the glory, and they were interceding for us to have revival, praying for us to have a glorious outpouring.

00:21:58.000 --> 00:21:58.547
And I'm telling you, they were assisting.

00:22:10.559 --> 00:22:11.188
And as they were praying, the glory was coming out of them, and it was coming on me.

00:22:19.977 --> 00:22:24.440
And that's what we were feeling in my house, and I could feel it bubbling up out of my spirit.

00:22:24.440 --> 00:22:28.040
I was underneath that presence all night long.

00:22:28.040 --> 00:22:31.360
I felt it; it was so strong, like a cloak.

00:22:35.280 --> 00:22:36.169
And the Lord kept showing me a cloak coming on me.

00:22:53.140 --> 00:22:57.154
I could see it.

00:22:57.154 --> 00:23:05.291
And I told Diana, I said, "Boy, it's increasing.

00:23:05.291 --> 00:23:21.200
" He said, "Heaven and earth are about to collide with the greatest harvest of souls and the greatest demonstrations and manifestations of My glory that this world has ever seen before.

00:23:21.200 --> 00:23:27.302
" In a 24-hour period, Brandon, we're at the point of no return.

00:23:27.302 --> 00:23:30.206
We're at that point.

00:23:30.206 --> 00:23:33.039
It's time to push.

00:23:33.039 --> 00:23:34.417
It's time to push.

00:23:34.417 --> 00:23:37.620
Do you understand what I'm trying to tell y'all?

00:23:50.944 --> 00:23:51.360
It's time.

00:24:06.903 --> 00:24:07.200
He said, "You're looking there at that thread, that thin thread.

00:24:07.200 --> 00:24:12.359
Remember that hair-thin thread when I said Adam's lease is coming up?

00:24:12.359 --> 00:24:13.850
" Do you understand?

00:24:13.850 --> 00:24:16.560
We're about to step over the water's edge.

00:24:16.560 --> 00:24:18.960
We're about to step over the waterfall.

00:24:20.080 --> 00:24:24.507
And the Lord told me, He said, "You are about to see something I longed for you to see.

00:24:24.507 --> 00:24:25.493
" Why?

00:24:25.493 --> 00:24:27.486
Because there was a lease.

00:24:27.486 --> 00:24:29.740
There was Adam's time frame of a 6,000-year window.

